# Liquid Templating Reference

## Basic Syntax

### Output (render values)
```liquid
{{ page.title }}
{{ site.title }}
{{ content }}
{{ product.price | default: "Contact us" }}
```

### Tags (logic)
```liquid
{% if condition %}...{% endif %}
{% for item in collection %}...{% endfor %}
{% include component.html %}
{% assign variable = value %}
```

## Conditionals

```liquid
{% if page.featured %}
  <span class="badge">Рекомендовано</span>
{% elsif page.new %}
  <span class="badge">Новинка</span>
{% else %}
  <span class="badge">Стандарт</span>
{% endif %}

{% unless page.hidden %}
  <!-- Show content -->
{% endunless %}

{% case page.category %}
  {% when "software" %}
    Software category
  {% when "hardware" %}
    Hardware category
  {% else %}
    Default
{% endcase %}
```

## Loops

```liquid
{% for product in site.products limit:6 %}
  {% if forloop.first %}<div class="featured">{% endif %}
  
  <div class="product">
    {{ product.title }}
    <!-- forloop.index (1-based), forloop.index0 (0-based) -->
    <!-- forloop.first, forloop.last, forloop.length -->
  </div>
  
  {% if forloop.last %}</div>{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
```

## Filters

### URL Filters
```liquid
{{ "/page" | relative_url }}      → /baseurl/page
{{ "/page" | absolute_url }}      → https://site.com/page
{{ page.url | prepend: site.url }}
```

### String Filters
```liquid
{{ "text" | upcase }}             → TEXT
{{ "TEXT" | downcase }}           → text
{{ "text" | capitalize }}         → Text
{{ "Page Title" | slugify }}      → page-title
{{ content | truncate: 100 }}     → First 100 chars...
{{ content | strip_html }}        → Remove HTML tags
{{ text | escape }}               → HTML escape
```

### Array Filters
```liquid
{{ site.products | where: "featured", true }}
{{ site.products | where_exp: "p", "p.price_value > 1000" }}
{{ site.products | sort: "order" }}
{{ site.products | reverse }}
{{ site.products | first }}
{{ site.products | last }}
{{ site.products | size }}
{{ array | join: ", " }}
{{ array | uniq }}
{{ array | concat: other_array }}
```

### Date Filters
```liquid
{{ page.date | date: "%d.%m.%Y" }}        → 22.01.2026
{{ page.date | date: "%B %d, %Y" }}       → January 22, 2026
{{ site.time | date: "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M" }}  → Build timestamp
```

### Content Filters
```liquid
{{ page.content | markdownify }}          → Markdown to HTML
{{ page.excerpt | strip_html | truncate: 160 }}
{{ content | number_of_words }}
```

## Variables

### Assign
```liquid
{% assign featured = site.products | where: "featured", true %}
{% assign count = site.products | size %}
```

### Capture (multiline)
```liquid
{% capture product_list %}
  {% for p in site.products %}
    {{ p.title }}{% unless forloop.last %}, {% endunless %}
  {% endfor %}
{% endcapture %}
{{ product_list | strip }}
```

## Include with Parameters

```liquid
{% include card.html 
   title=product.title 
   image=product.image 
   url=product.url 
   class="featured"
%}
```

In include file, access via `include.param`:

```html
<!-- _includes/card.html -->
<div class="card {{ include.class }}">
  <img src="{{ include.image }}" alt="{{ include.title }}">
  <h3>{{ include.title }}</h3>
  <a href="{{ include.url }}">Детальніше</a>
</div>
```

