```

## Common Patterns

### Navigation with Active State
```liquid
{% for item in site.data.navigation.main %}
  <a href="{{ item.url }}" 
     {% if page.url == item.url %}class="active"{% endif %}>
    {{ item.title }}
  </a>
{% endfor %}
```

### Conditional Default Image
```liquid
{% if product.image %}
  <img src="{{ product.image }}" alt="{{ product.title }}">
{% else %}
  <img src="/assets/images/default-product.png" alt="Product">
{% endif %}
```

### Group by Category
```liquid
{% assign grouped = site.products | group_by: "category" %}
{% for group in grouped %}
  <h2>{{ group.name }}</h2>
  {% for product in group.items %}
    {{ product.title }}
  {% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
```
